          "definition": "n. 租賃、租金、出租物  a. 租賃的、收取租金的"
        }
      ],
      "examples": [
        {
          "en": "The monthly rental for a one-bedroom apartment downtown has doubled in five years.",
          "highlight": [
            "rental"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "市中心一房公寓的月租金在五年內翻了一倍。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "Long-term rentals are usually cheaper than short-term leases when averaged per night.",
          "highlight": [
            "rentals"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "長期租賃平均到每晚的費用通常比短期租約便宜。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "Rental cars must be returned with a full tank of gas to avoid extra charges.",
          "highlight": [
            "Rental"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "租來的車必須加滿油才能歸還，以避免額外收費。"
          }
        }
      ],
