        {
          "en": "Cafeterias in hospitals often stay open twenty-four hours for night shift staff.",
          "highlight": [
            "Cafeterias"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "醫院的自助餐廳通常為夜班員工二十四小時營業。"
